Rules.InvariantScript: "Are you sure you want to close the application?"

Set(gblAppVersion, "v2.2.1");
// declare app cache schema
Set(gblAppCache,
    {
        CacheExists: false,
        CacheVersion: gblAppVersion,
        CacheLastRefreshed: DateAdd(Now(), -100, TimeUnit.Years),
        UserEmail: "",
        FnOUserId: "",
        IsUserMaintenanceWorker: false,
        IsUserMaintenanceRequester: false,
        UserPersonnelNumber: "",

        UserActiveWorker: Defaults('Asset management maintenance workers (mserp)')
    }
);
// declare language choice schema
Set(gblLanguageCode, Language());
// attempt to load user language selection
IfError(
    // try:
    LoadData(colLanguageChoice, "AppLanguageChoice", true),
        // on error:
        Trace("Unable to load AppLanguageChoice", ErrorSeverity.Warning, FirstError), // this always occurs in PApp Studio, ignore
    // then do:
    Set(gblLanguageCode, First(colLanguageChoice).Value)
);
Set(C,
    {
        EmDash: "—",
        FnOErrorRegex: "\""code"":""(?<code>[^""]*)"",""message"":""(?<message>[^""]*)",

            PivotOnWorkOrders: "workorders",
            PivotOnJobs: "jobs",
            SortByWorkOrderId: "workorderid",
            SortByWorkOrderServiceLevel: "workorderservicelevel",
            SortByWorkStartDate: "workstartdate",
            FilterByToday: "today",
            FilterByThisWeek: "thisweek",
            FilterByAllTime: "alltime",

                ShowWorkOrderOrMaintenanceRequestChoice: "choose",
                ShowWorkOrderCreation: "workorder",

        WorkOrderDetailsScreen: {
            DetailsSubPage: "details",
            JobsSubPage: "jobs"
        },
        WorkOrderJobDetailsScreen: {
            DetailsSubPage: "details",
            ChecklistSubPage: "checklist"

            SearchAllItems: "items",
            SearchSpareParts: "spareparts",
            SearchAssetBOM: "assetbom"

            SearchFunctionalLocations: "functionallocations",

            CreateFromAsset: "asset",
            CreateFromLocation: "location",
            CreateWorkOrder: "createworkorder",
            CreateMaintenanceRequest: "createmaintenancerequest"
        }
    }
);
// declare work order overview pivot schema
ClearCollect(colWorkOrdersPivotChoice, {Value:C.WorkOrdersScreen.PivotOnJobs}); // this is needed for some reason, to statically declare the collection type
Clear(colWorkOrdersPivotChoice); // this is needed since LoadData will append to the collection
// attempt to load user work order overview pivot selection
IfError(
    // try:
    LoadData(colWorkOrdersPivotChoice, "AppWorkOrdersPivotChoice", true),
        // on error:
        Trace("Unable to load AppWorkOrdersPivotChoice", ErrorSeverity.Warning, FirstError); // this always occurs in PApp Studio, ignore
        Set(gblWorkOrdersPivotChoice, C.WorkOrdersScreen.PivotOnJobs),
    // then do:
    With({ locWorkOrdersPivotChoice: First(colWorkOrdersPivotChoice).Value },
        Trace("Work orders pivot choice", TraceSeverity.Information, { Value: locWorkOrdersPivotChoice });
        Set(gblWorkOrdersPivotChoice, Coalesce(locWorkOrdersPivotChoice, C.WorkOrdersScreen.PivotOnJobs))
    );
);
